** About Us: **   
  
Our client is on a large-scale Digital Transformation journey to revolutionize
their systems and empower their workforce with cutting-edge technology
solutions. As part of this large scale transformation will be relocating their
Infrastructure to the cloud, enabling enhanced security, resilience, and
innovation.  
  
** Job Description: **   
  
We are seeking a talented Cloud Control Analyst/ Specialist to join our team
and play a crucial role in the digital transformation journey. As a Cloud
Specialist, you will be responsible for leading the migration of our on-site
data and applications to a secure cloud-based environment.  
Key responsibilities:  

  * Design and implement cloud-based solutions to support our business objectives. 
  * Provide documentation and support to ensure a smooth migration and ongoing management of cloud-based services. 
  * Collaborate with project managers and stakeholders to support project delivery and ensure alignment with business goals. 
  * Conduct a thorough assessment and analysis of the CSA Cloud Controls Matrix (CCM) to ensure compliance with cybersecurity standards and regulations relevant to cloud computing environments. 
  * Proven experience in cloud migration projects, with a strong understanding of cloud technologies and best practices. 
  * Excellent documentation skills and experience working in a Business Analyst role. 
